text: Anante Ra Anumzamo'a Josuana amanage huno asami'ne, ko'ma tamagra Isipima mani'neta kazokzo eri'zama eneritma tamagazegu hu'nazane. Hianagi Nagra menina tamagri tamagaze zana eri netroe. Hige'za ana kumakura Gilgalie5:9 Gilgaliema hu'neana Hibru kefina agaze eri atrene hu'ne. hu'za agia antemi'nageno, ana agimo'a meninena meno e'ne.
